statements: SELECT user_id, access_level FROM palm_vein_recognition_data;
SELECT * FROM palm_vein_recognition_data WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT DISTINCT access_level FROM palm_vein_recognition_data ORDER BY access_level DESC;
SELECT user_id, timestamp FROM palm_vein_recognition_data WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT user_id, access_level, vein_pattern FROM palm_vein_recognition_data ORDER BY user_id DESC, access_level ASC;
SELECT * FROM palm_vein_recognition_data WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT user_id, timestamp FROM palm_vein_recognition_data WHERE access_level = 3 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, access_level FROM palm_vein_recognition_data WHERE access_level >= 2 ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT user_id, timestamp FROM palm_vein_recognition_data WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' AND access_level < 4;
SELECT * FROM palm_vein_recognition_data WHERE access_level = 1 OR access_level = 3 ORDER BY user_id;
SELECT * FROM PalmVeinRecognition;
SELECT user_id, vein_data FROM PalmVeinRecognition WHERE id = 1;
SELECT user_id, timestamp FROM SecurityAuditTrail WHERE activity = 'Login';
SELECT * FROM SecurityAuditTrail ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM PalmVeinRecognition WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM PalmVeinRecognition WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, user_id FROM PalmVeinRecognition WHERE vein_data IS NOT NULL ORDER BY id ASC, timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM SecurityAuditTrail WHERE activity LIKE '%Login%' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT audit_id, user_id, timestamp FROM SecurityAuditTrail WHERE user_id = 3 ORDER BY audit_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM PalmVeinRecognition WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' ORDER BY user_id ASC, timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, user_id, timestamp FROM palm_vein_recognition_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM palm_vein_recognition_data WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000'
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) FROM access_logs GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 3
SELECT * FROM audit_trails ORDER BY timestamp ASC, audit_id DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT action, timestamp FROM audit_trails WHERE user_id = '5532805c-c7d9-4a66-b616-7c4e521d8cfe' ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT id, user_id, vein_data, timestamp FROM palm_vein_recognition_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT * FROM access_logs WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000' AND access_type = 'Login' ORDER BY access_time ASC
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_access FROM access_logs GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY total_access DESC
SELECT audit_id, action, timestamp, user_id FROM audit_trails WHERE action LIKE '%update%' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT user_id, vein_data FROM palm_vein_recognition_data WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND timestamp <= '2022-01-31 23:59:59' ORDER BY timestamp ASC
SELECT user_id, username FROM palm_vein_users;
SELECT access_time, success FROM access_logs ORDER BY access_time DESC;
SELECT user_id, access_time, success FROM access_logs WHERE success = true;
SELECT user_id, level_name FROM palm_vein_users JOIN user_roles ON palm_vein_users.user_id = user_roles.user_id JOIN security_levels ON user_roles.role_name = security_levels.level_name;
SELECT * FROM security_levels WHERE level_name LIKE 'Admin%';
SELECT * FROM palm_vein_users WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT user_id, username FROM palm_vein_users ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT access_time, success FROM access_logs WHERE user_id IN (SELECT user_id FROM user_roles WHERE role_name = 'Admin');
SELECT pvu.username, al.access_time FROM palm_vein_users pvu JOIN access_logs al ON pvu.user_id = al.user_id WHERE al.success = true;
SELECT sl.level_name, ur.role_name FROM security_levels sl JOIN user_roles ur ON sl.level_id = ur.role_id;
SELECT * FROM User;
SELECT username, security_level FROM User;
SELECT user_id, username FROM User WHERE security_level > 2;
SELECT * FROM AccessLog WHERE access_result = 'SUCCESS';
SELECT user_id, action, timestamp FROM AuditTrail ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM User;
SELECT user_id, username FROM User ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT user_id, username, security_level FROM User WHERE security_level > 5;
SELECT u.user_id, u.username, a.action, a.timestamp FROM User u INNER JOIN AuditTrail a ON u.user_id = a.user_id;
SELECT u.username, a.timestamp, al.access_result FROM User u LEFT JOIN AuditTrail a ON u.user_id = a.user_id LEFT JOIN AccessLog al ON u.user_id = al.user_id ORDER BY a.timestamp DESC;
